Hey, you know there's a really nice
Saffronia tree round here?

rows.label: kizunainn067_msg0002
rows.name:

Blossomshade Cliff and
take a look? It won't take long.

rows.label: kizunainn067_msg0003

Pleeeease! Come on, won't you come
and take a look?
